    (select l.*, icf."the_geom" as geom from "public"."lieux_prep_rn_with_city_code" l, "public"."ign_commune_france" icf where l."current_city_code" = icf."INSEE_COM"),
bornes as 
    (select b.*, icf."the_geom" as geom from "public"."bornes_routes_borne_suivante_2016" b, "public"."ign_commune_france" icf where b."INSEE_COM" = icf."INSEE_COM")

FROM lieux l
LEFT JOIN bornes b
ON 
    (l.catr = 'autoroute' OR l.catr = "route nationale") 
    AND l."voie_normalise" = b."nom_courant_route" 
    AND l.pr = b.pr 
    AND ST_DWithin(l.geom::geography, b.geom::geography, 2000)

SELECT DISTINCT ON (l."Num_Acc") l.*, b.lat, b.lon, b.lat_next, b.lon_next, b."INSEE_COM" as pr_insee_com, b."NOM_COM" as pr_nom_com

    AND l."voie_normalise" = b."nom_courant_route" 
    AND l.pr = b.pr 
    AND ST_DWithin(l.geom::geography, b.geom::geography, 2000)
order by l."Num_Acc", ST_distance(l.geom, b.geom)
limit 100
